com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.places.autocomplete

Class PlaceAutocomplete.IntentBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapbox.mapboxsdk.plugins.places.autocomplete.PlaceAutocomplete.IntentBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    PlaceAutocomplete

    public static class PlaceAutocomplete.IntentBuilder
extends Object
    Builder for the Place Autocomplete launch intent.

    After setting the required and optional parameters, call build(Activity) and pass the intent to Activity.startActivityForResult(Intent, int).

    Since:
    0.1.0
